{"msg_id":"a674a27e-8345-45dc-b49f-f07265c9a0fa","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775663363261361899,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"5/6 done conditions verified in code with tests. Cross-campfire ref resolution (state.go, crossdep.go), show display (show.go), TOFU pinning (join.go) all implemented and tested. Remaining gap: multi-root resolution and beacon failover in rd join — deferred to follow-up items.","resolution":"done","target":"82757c63-2171-49ae-a790-55713c5fc4a2"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
