{"msg_id":"0b350895-47c3-41e4-aa93-2f6370d8e145","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775676200094758969,"operation":"work:create","payload":{"for":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd","id":"ready-7bb","priority":"p0","title":"Hosted path broken: rd join doesn't bootstrap project, members can't close items, sync pull incomplete","type":"bug"},"tags":["work:create"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
{"msg_id":"da1064eb-cd72-4682-8cec-fdb1437bcdca","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775676223252489419,"operation":"work:update","payload":{"context":"## Context\nFound during v0.8.0 hosted demo testing against mcp.getcampfire.dev. Three bugs make the hosted multi-machine path non-functional:\n\n1. rd join doesn't bootstrap .ready/ — member has no local project state after joining\n2. work:close rejected for admitted members — provenance level 1 insufficient for level-2 operations\n3. rd sync pull incomplete — doesn't pull enough messages for item to appear in rd ready\n\nThese block demos 07 (hosted real-time), 08 (org naming), and 10 (bridge hybrid). Filesystem demos 01-06 all pass clean on v0.8.0.\n\n## Reproduction\nMachine A (owner): cf init --remote, rd init --name test --confirm, rd admit MEMBER_KEY, rd create item.\nMachine B (member): cf init --remote, rd join CAMPFIRE_ID.\nBUG 1: no .ready/ created. rd sync pull fails. rd ready shows nothing.\nEven with manual .ready/ setup: rd sync pull pulls 1 msg (BUG 3), rd done rejected at provenance level (BUG 2).\n\n## Done condition\nAll three bugs fixed. Demo 07 runs end-to-end: owner creates item on Machine A, member syncs and sees it on Machine B, member claims and closes, owner syncs and sees completion.","target":"0b350895-47c3-41e4-aa93-2f6370d8e145"},"tags":["work:update"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
{"msg_id":"154a927d-4f30-4b1c-8831-7f2fa1836da3","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775676230087778677,"operation":"work:create","payload":{"for":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd","id":"ready-357","priority":"p0","title":"BUG: rd join doesn't bootstrap .ready/ project directory for joiners","type":"task"},"tags":["work:create"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
