{"msg_id":"da176665-ca0c-4c94-8e6c-dbb9d46c2535","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775676287522898634,"operation":"work:update","payload":{"context":"## Context\nv0.8.0 tagged. Filesystem demos 01-06 pass clean from fresh install. Hosted demos blocked by ready-7bb (3 bugs). After bugs fixed, build and test hosted demos, then extract website examples from validated transcripts.\n\n## Filesystem demos (DONE — transcripts in test/demo/output/)\n01-solo: Solo dev lifecycle. PASS.\n02-team: Two-identity admit/join/delegate. PASS.\n03-multiproject: Cross-project dependencies. PASS.\n04-org-observer: Read-only summary access. PASS.\n05-agent-workflow: Programmatic agent access. PASS.\n06-gate-escalation: Human approval gates. PASS.\n\n## Hosted demos (BLOCKED by ready-7bb)\n07-hosted-realtime: Two identities on mcp.getcampfire.dev, separate project dirs, sync pull, full lifecycle.\n08-org-naming: rd register --org, name resolution across projects on hosted infra.\n10-bridge-hybrid: Local filesystem dev synced to hosted relay via cf bridge.\n\n## Website update\nExtract tested terminal examples from all demo transcripts. Update site/index.html with real, validated command output. Each example traceable to a demo script that ran against v0.8.0.","target":"116ad5f7-d95d-43c3-a07c-2342717efd03"},"tags":["work:update"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
