{"msg_id":"766471c9-fcf5-4c5f-8004-53226951bc68","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775691426168158229,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Implemented bootstrapJoinedProject() in join.go with auto-sync pull via clientLister. rd join now creates .campfire/root, .ready/config.json, and .ready/mutations.jsonl, then pulls existing campfire items so rd list shows them immediately without manual rd sync pull. Pull failures non-fatal. TestE2E_JoinAutoSyncPull added and passing. PR #44.","resolution":"done","target":"611e49fa-8ebb-4d3c-a7ce-5b4a6688c388"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
