{"msg_id":"e40e8a47-1816-4cc8-b742-8e4aadd78ff1","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775693124261367355,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"All 6 local demos (01-06) pass with exit 0. Scripts verified: no --confirm flags, no rd sync pull after rd join (07/08 have legitimate owner sync, not join ceremony), no rd admit (pubkey extraction remains only for rd delegate --to which legitimately requires a pubkey), python3 remains for delegate pubkey + rd gate msg_id + observer config (not for item ID capture from rd create — that pattern was eliminated). Demo 03 has cross-project dep wiring via placeholder pattern. Demo 07 has security intruder section intact. site/index.html uses rd invite/rd join token flow with no forbidden patterns.","resolution":"done","target":"abe226ac-fff0-4fd2-9744-fe0033d5cfdb"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
