{"msg_id":"32887ef3-b5b5-4a9b-851a-f1074c1383c3","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775695746567995405,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Fixed unit mismatch: IsSoloMode now uses UnixNano() to match ensureServerBinding. Stale bindings from crashed servers now expire correctly. Regression test added (TestIsSoloMode_NanosecondUnitConsistency). PR: https://github.com/campfire-net/ready/pull/48","resolution":"done","target":"73c86edb-e810-406d-ab49-d5fd0c667d9a"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
{"msg_id":"569b3a07-5c45-4222-8669-46775b0b13fe","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775696053433373860,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Fixed: PersistentPreRunE now skips protocol.Init for rdx1_ token joins, eliminating the --force requirement on fresh CF_HOME. Regression test covers all 3 scenarios. PR: https://github.com/campfire-net/ready/pull/49","resolution":"done","target":"371df94e-cc37-479d-bc5f-d1954a6af4aa"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
{"msg_id":"d717f817-d819-42b3-aa4a-43f82d7842da","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775696238749322242,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Implemented walk-up identity resolution in CFHome(). Detection order: flag → CF_HOME env → walk-up .cf/identity.json from cwd → ~/.cf → ~/.campfire → default ~/.cf. 7 new tests + 7 existing tests all passing. PR #50.","resolution":"done","target":"174d0e21-5ffb-4433-baf2-e6c8a5c94b73"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
{"msg_id":"b240a03b-3e4c-4335-bf63-b9b361aa4bac","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775696413891201006,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Implemented pipe-friendly output for rd ready and rd list. When stdout is not a TTY, both commands print one bare ID per line (no table formatting) so scripts can use $(rd ready) or $(rd list) to get IDs. JSON output unchanged. Matches rd create behavior (ready-e09). PR: https://github.com/campfire-net/ready/pull/51","resolution":"done","target":"fabca58e-49c3-4bf6-bbe2-16bb63ef3abe"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
