{"msg_id":"d27ff031-5d8a-438e-afb8-b34c45eb999e","campfire_id":"670f815159f88220981e79b7cbbc5e98432d73771c215b7d2082ec818b74329a","timestamp":1775696787152585318,"operation":"work:close","payload":{"reason":"Demo 03 rewritten to demonstrate real cross-project deps (rd dep add wires cross-campfire blocking). Fixed two bugs found during implementation: (1) allItemsFromJSONLOrStore was not calling crossdep.ApplyBlocking in JSONL mode — cross-campfire deps had no effect on rd ready; (2) block.json max_length for blocker_id was 64, too short for cross-campfire ref format (~85 chars). All tests pass. PR: https://github.com/campfire-net/ready/pull/52","resolution":"done","target":"ee4d7818-49b7-4213-ad11-35bdbc7a249c"},"tags":["work:close"],"sender":"1e224c14bc7959bf6bec7d4e563389b6c3d3e9255ad206df1ba60cdc52197ffd"}
